Name: Combo Assault
Desc:
[Enchant Force]
Attacks the nearby enemy with a bow, and then shoots an arrow flying through space to attack a wide range of enemies.
Discharge Enhancement
Arrows deal damage to enemies in a wider range.
Blast Enhancement
Performs a powerful strike to an enemy with your bow.
Transition Enhancement
Gives multiple Ancient Curse Debuff stacks to enemies damaged by your bow attack.

H.Old:
Relic Gauge Cost: 100. Bow attack deals damage to up to 4 enemies at 500% damage 7 times. Damaged enemies are inflicted with 1 stacks of the Ancient Curse Debuff.
Arrows deal damage up to 10 enemies at 550% damage 5 times.
Cooldown: 20 sec.
